cross: Cattleya Seagulls Apricot x Cattleya Circle of Life

measurements.description: Two flowers on one 11-cm inflorescence; sepals apricot veined red; petals apricot veined red, splashed darker red fanning midline to apex; lip bright yellow, midlobe fully flushed intense crimson; column pale pink, anther cap white; substance firm; texture crystalline.
